This is a basic Monk skeleton for Sinatra.

Please remember to launch this app via config.ru:
$ bundle exec thin -p 4567 -R config.ru start

You will find your running app at:
http://127.0.0.1:4567

Init a project:
# Before creating your project
monk add riblits git://github.com/muccy/riblits.git

# Inside your empty project directory
monk init -s riblits
